---
import joe from '../assets/joe_kidushim.jpg';
---
<section class="section-bg-light">
    <div class="title-color pt-10 text-2xl md:text-4xl bg-blend-color text-center w-full md:w-3/4 mx-auto">
        40+ Years of Industry Expertise At Your Service
    </div>
    <div class="py-10 border-b-1 border-b-[#3A6EA5] flex flex-col md:flex-row w-full md:w-3/4 mx-auto items-start">
        <div class="md:w-[30%] w-full flex flex-col items-center mb-6 md:mb-0">
            <img src={joe.src} alt="Joseph A. Kidushim"
                 class="w-full h-auto max-w-xs md:max-w-none object-cover"/>
            <div class="mt-4 text-lg font-semibold text-center">Joseph A. Kidushim</div>
        </div>
        <div class="md:w-[70%] w-full md:pl-8 text-base md:text-lg flex items-center">
            With 35+ years in the insurance industry, Joseph A. Kidushim has helped clients across the country secure
            their financial future with life insurance and retirement solutions. A top-producing agent and MDRT award
            recipient, Joe combines expert knowledge with a personal, client-first approach. Whether planning for your
            family’s protection or your retirement, Joe makes complex decisions simple, helping you choose the right
            coverage for your needs. Outside of work, he’s active in his community, enjoys cycling, kayaking, and
            cooking, and cherishes time with his wife, three sons, and grandchildren.
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="py-10 flex flex-col md:flex-row w-full md:w-3/4 mx-auto items-start">
        <div class="md:w-[30%] w-full flex flex-col items-center mb-6 md:mb-0">
            <img src="/joe_kidushim.jpg" alt="Ernesto Peimbert"
                 class="w-full h-auto rounded-full max-w-xs md:max-w-none object-cover"/>
            <div class="mt-4 text-lg font-semibold text-center">Ernesto Peimbert</div>
        </div>
        <div class="md:w-[70%] w-full md:pl-8 text-base md:text-lg flex items-center">
            ERNESTO????
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
